This directory contains automation scripts for the project.

## Scripts

### `publish-to-framer.js`
Publishes articles from Supabase to Framer CMS using the Framer Server API.

See the [README](./README.md) for full documentation.

## Setup

```bash
cd scripts
npm install
cp .env.local.example .env.local
# Edit .env.local with your credentials
```

## Quick Start

```bash
npm run publish:framer
```
